<translate>
'''VRCat''' is the official mascot of [[Special:MyLanguage/VRChat|VRChat]], a spacefaring orange cat with white markings. He wears a box on his head, with the [[Special:MyLanguage/VRC+]] symbol on the side.

== Appearances ==
VRCat's first appearance was [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z-MKanCkDck Introducing VRChat Plus] and has been seen in numerous official VRChat announcements and social media posts since.

VRCat appears as the Early Supporter [[Special:MyLanguage/Badges|Badge]] for users who bought [[Special:MyLanguage/VRC+]] when it was first released. The badge can be pet on a user's profile on the website.

After purchasing VRC+, VRCat will appear on the user's [[Special:MyLanguage/Quick Menu]]. Clicking VRCat in this menu multiple times will cause dialogue to appear.<!-- any misspellings or grammatical errors in the dialogue table below are how they are displayed in-game -->
